<paragraph id="477D125BE06BF334E7A3FD59D3535107" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3122260683F1A11AEEFB94C825AF9BC1" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Centred on Bahia State, Brazil this species is widespread on the borders of scrub and woodland at the transition from the cerrado to caatinga biomes. There is a smaller disjunct population on the borders of Paraguay and Mato Grosso do Sul state.</paragraph>
